{"tid":159972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【保良局醜聞】負責人稱新一代玻璃心 鄭中基：我同你玩一次，你做學生！","createTime":"2017-03-17T11:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T00:08:41.000Z","uid":37524,"like":74,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b2c2832e22f1625163346b92e4622efbd7f0f1","tid":159972,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"寸過創科局局長楊偉雄「冇腦、onX無極限、X到漏汁，又話講緊廣東話，但冇人聽得明嘅創科局局長?」<br />\n<br />\n吳克儉爆轉校論，話家長唔滿意學校操TSA，可以唔去讀同轉校，佢即喺facebook大鬧「咩教育局長會教家長咁做」，嘆「唔得掂你個X樣係得嘅」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n呢個人就係「暴龍哥」鄭中基!<br />\n鄭中基一向喺facebook不平則鳴，有時都幾語出驚人，再加上佢同老婆余思敏，育有一對仔女，所以鄭中基更加關心香港嘅學童問題!<br />\n近日保良局領袖紀律訓練營接連爆出涉嫌虐待學生醜聞，該營項目總監盧錦昌同時為外判承辦商「導航訓練中心」負責人，接受《蘋果》專訪時，否認所有指控，「如果我哋做到咁（虐待），有邊間學校會制？」又指年輕一代受家長溺愛，心靈太脆弱，玻璃心，「泥沙塗面」屬軍訓；被指向學生施虐嘅副總監梁永樂則稱冇迫學生食草，亦冇用粗言辱罵學生，而女教練Gloria都否認曾罵學生「廢柴」或「廢人」<br />\n鄭中基下午5點幾喺facebook留言：「玻璃心呀嗱？你聯絡我，我同你玩一次，你做學生！」佢同網民一齊plan點做訓練員&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n有網民就叫俾佢哋食牛歡喜，仲要「唔準切，唔準洗」，鄭中基回覆：「牛歡喜sashimi!」另一網民就叫：「要佢x騾！」鄭中基回應：「唔准飲咗酒x。」<br />\n唔少網民表示支持「林鄭」&hellip;唔係講嗰個，係「林敏聰+鄭中基」去做訓練員。<br />\n《蘋果》聯絡過鄭中基，鄭中基透過經理人講：「佢冇回應啦!」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170317/56442320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170317%2F56442320&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=be7b6e41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170317%2F56442320&h=2aa5d7b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170317/56442320</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170317/large/1489747312_aacc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170317%2Flarge%2F1489747312_aacc.jpg&h=0654d6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170317/large/1489747953_0411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170317%2Flarge%2F1489747953_0411.jpg&h=08cb2f88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170317/large/1489747954_c935.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170317%2Flarge%2F1489747954_c935.jpg&h=cba63f39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"978c176b989793590d93bdfecc2f9feb083c2d8b","tid":159972,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:48:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"186f902694cff59e63f7281183f89253dc9c6216","tid":159972,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"暴龍哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09dc939e299f8c14bdac68094b118791295b630b","tid":159972,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8d3ef506f6141db82a322f821606756248042d4","tid":159972,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4r9Lr96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4r9Lr96.jpg&h=5b3248d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實依張咩事"},{"pid":"f1d48c45e7916082bea1baa96b0c152572544f27","tid":159972,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4r9Lr96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4r9Lr96.jpg&h=5b3248d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實依張咩事</blockquote><br />\n j圖"},{"pid":"2945437257f7865fc9d5cbb1b1fc0c27c977bd76","tid":159972,"uid":20846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"有邊位學員可以出黎示範"},{"pid":"c727dbde98ebbc32d4cff8e4fab06fddecc94cbd","